  <div class="col-xs-12">
    <h3 class="center"><%= current_user.username %> Closet</h3>

  <% if @pictures.any? %>
    <% @pictures.each do |picture| %>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">

        <div class="well">
          <%= image_tag picture.image, :class => "image-size img-responsive round" %>
        <div id="block1">
          <span class="month"><%= picture.created_at.strftime("%b") %></span>
          <span class="day"><%= picture.created_at.strftime("%d") %></span>
          <div class="title"><%= picture.title %></div>
          <div class="description"><%= picture.description %></div>
        </div>

        <div id="block2">
          <%= link_to image_tag("btn-fav.png", :class => 'fav-button'), {:fav => picture.id} %><br><br>
          <!-- <span class="vote-number"><%= picture.get_likes.size %></span> -->
          <%= link_to image_tag("btn-edit.png", :alt => "edit", :class => "marginL edit-button"), picture_path(picture) %>
        </div>

        <div id="block-bottom">
          <%# link_to "Show Details", :class => "center  btn", :showdetail => "showdetail" %>
          <!-- <span class="time"><%# time_ago_in_words(picture.created_at) %></span> -->
        </div>

        <% if @showdetail === true %>
          <div id="details"><hr>
            <% if picture.body != "" %>
              <span class="type">Body:</span> <span class="detail"><%= picture.body %></span><br>
            <% end %>
            <% if picture.legs != ""  %>
              <span class="type">Legs:</span> <span class="detail"> <%= picture.legs %></span><br>
            <% end %>
            <% if picture.feet != "" %>
              <span class="type">Feet:</span> <span class="detail"> <%= picture.feet %></span><br>
            <% end %>
            <% if picture.hands != "" %>
              <span class="type">Hands:</span> <span class="detail"> <%= picture.hands %></span><br>
            <% end %>
            <% if picture.head != "" %>
              <span class="type">Head:</span> <span class="detail"> <%= picture.head %></span><br>
            <% end %>
          </div><!-- detail end -->
        <% end %><!-- showdetail end -->
        </div><!-- well end -->
      </div><!-- col end -->
        <% end %>
  <% else %>
    <div class="tutorial"><br><br>
      <span class=""><h3>Welcome to Closets!</h3></span>
      <h5>This app allows you to save a record of your outfits so you never have to worry about wearing the same thing twice.</h5>
      <h2>How this works!</h2>
      <h4>1. You can press the <%= link_to image_tag("btn-photo-tut.png", :id => "photo-button", :class => "btn photo-button-tut"), new_picture_path %> below and take a selfie of your outfit. Give it a title and save it.</h4>
      <h4>2. Once the outfit is saved you can view it on your home page <%= link_to image_tag("btn-home-tut.png", :class => "home-button-tut"), pictures_path %></h4>
      <h4>3. While viewing the outfit... if you press the pin needle   <%= image_tag("btn-edit-tut.png", :alt => "edit", :class => "edit-button-tut") %> you can add more details to the outfit such as color of shirt of type of shoes.. etc.</h4>
      <h4>4. While adding details to your outfit you can also add events. Events work like categories and you can view them on the events page. <%= link_to image_tag("btn-event-tut.png", :class => "event-button-tut"), events_path %></h4>
    </div>
  <% end %>
</div> <!-- col end -->
